    "We use the terminology of the UK Defence Intelligence Probability Yardstick 50 to specify our level of certainty.",
    "This yardstick splits the probability scale into seven ranges: remote chance (0-5%); highly unlikely 50 Ministry of Defence. 2023.",
    "\"Defence Intelligence -communicating probability.\"",
    "https://www.gov.uk/government/news/defence-intelligence-communicating-probability (10-20%); unlikely (25-35%); realistic possibility (40-50%); likely (55-75%); highly likely (80-90%); almost certain (95-100%) ‡.",
